To start off the week, take it slow and easy with this fancy version of a hot dog. This cheesy boerewors chilli dog can be made within an hour and will please your family and guests.  A recipe created by the popular flame-grilled chicken franchise, Nando’s, this cheesy boerewors chilli dog recipe can be substituted in terms of the meat.  Instead of cooking the boerewors, you can use sausages, viennas or vegan alternatives. Serves: 4 Preparation: 10 minutes Cook: 40 minutes ALSO TRY: Three proudly South African hot dog recipes to create this weekend Preparations: 10 minutes Cook: 40 minutes  This recipe is courtesy of Nando’s South Africa. YOU MAY ALSO LIKE: Recipe of the day: Viral ‘two ingredient’ cheesy potato bread